Aproveite.

"3 Psychedelic Paths" is a small visual EP created to generate a visual/sound dive. Psychedelic ambient soundtrack composed using modular synthesizer and traditional instruments (Viola caipira, Flute and Guitar), 3D modeling created by Daniel Teolfe on top of each track to create an even deeper journey. Enjoy.
